trans-unit.source: Defines the binding element used to create a Peer Name Resolution Protocol (PNRP) peer resolver.
trans-unit.target: 이름 확인 프로토콜 PNRP (피어) 피어 확인자를 만드는 사용 되는 바인딩 요소를 정의 합니다.

trans-unit.source: To create a peer resolver from an instance of this class, call <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.PnrpPeerResolverBindingElement.CreatePeerResolver%2A> after the instance has been constructed.
trans-unit.target: 이 클래스의 인스턴스에서 피어 확인자를 만들려면 호출 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.PnrpPeerResolverBindingElement.CreatePeerResolver%2A>인스턴스에 생성 된 후.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.PnrpPeerResolverBindingElement.CreatePeerResolver%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new default instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.PnrpPeerResolverBindingElement"></xref> class.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.PnrpPeerResolverBindingElement"></xref> class with the provided peer referral policy.
trans-unit.target: 새 인스턴스를 초기화는 <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.PnrpPeerResolverBindingElement"> </xref> 제공 된 피어 조회 정책 사용 하 여 클래스입니다.
